HEADWORD: nonimmune
<hw>nonimmune</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Not having
immunity; susceptible; likely to be affected with, if exposed.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> liable to(predicate), nonresistant, unresistant,
susceptible to(predicate).</syn>⟦br⟧
